Some important Event classes and interfaces:
-------------------------------------------

1. ActionEvent -> generated when button is pressed, menu-item is selected, list-item is double clicked.
   Listener Interface -> ActionListener

2. MouseEvent -> generated when mouse is dragged, moved, clicked, pressed or released also when enters or exits a component.
   Listener Interface -> MouseListener

3. KeyEvent -> generated when input is received from keyboard
   Listener Interface ->  KeyListener

4. ItemEvent -> generated when check-box or list item is clicked
   Listener Interface -> ItemListener

5. TextEvent -> generated when value of textarea or text field is changed.
   Listener Interface -> TextListener

6. MouseWheelEvent -> generated when mouse wheel is moved
   Listener Interface -> MouseWheelListener

7. WindowEvent -> generated when window is activated, deactivated, de iconified, iconified, opened or closed.
   Listener Interface -> WindowListener

8. ComponentEvent -> generated when component is hidden, moved, resized or set visible.
   Listener Interface -> ComponentEventListener

9. ContainerEvent -> generated when component is added or removed from container.
   Listener Interface ->  ContainerListener
